			<div class="content" id="post-content-3981096">
									

<p>Well, the thing is that the Foundation as an organization never knew about 3448. All of Project Dammerung was kept a secret, so when Emily and everyone was told to jump ship, they didn't do the most thorough clean up. Emily destroyed a lot of the evidence, but she didn't destroy the machine. And it's not like they could've moved it either, it's a massive machine. So the best course of action, since Emily didn't want to destroy it, was to just leave it there.</p>

